{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body>\n\n<p>發佈時間：13:00 2026-04-27 HKT</p>\n<img alt=\"李連杰63歲生日被細女「突襲」  父女互動曝光  被嚇到「回春」揭真實狀態？\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl_square/0de457dff8a74ffce62d630373fd41da/2026-04/KF_103.jpg\"/>\n<p>金像影帝李連杰昨日（26日）63歲生日，在社交平台分享一段溫馨的慶生影片，當中見到李連杰獲細女Jada驚喜準備蛋糕，場面溫馨又有趣，李連杰更展現出燦爛笑容，可見心情極佳。</p>\n<h2>李連杰父女互動有趣</h2>\n<p>李連杰昨日在IG分享的新影片，見到閉上雙眼的他，在細女扶住坐到餐枱位置，前面有一個精緻的朱古力蛋糕，略顯老態的李連杰，神情平靜，任由女兒Jada為他布置。李連杰細女Jada俏皮地為爸爸戴上生日帽，又將蠟燭插在父親的手指之間，點上蠟燭後才抽出插到蛋糕上。</p>\n<p>Jada之後叫李連杰睜開眼，同時拉響禮炮，金色彩紙從天而降，李連杰一臉驚喜，表情逗趣展露出如孩童般的燦爛笑容。李連杰又雙手合十，許願後吹熄蠟燭，全程心情大好，舉動活潑，與過往的他判若兩人。</p>\n<p>相關閱讀：李連杰健康狀況急轉直下？面色發黑現身星洲法會 曾被傳「換心回春」後容光煥發</p>\n<img alt=\"李連杰減產後休養生息。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/327f3b6e928f59608c616d79ae8fbce2/2024-04/jetli_434322518_18335077330141665_7221379850240795299_n.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰積極行善，打理由其成立的壹基金。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a0f241ba9d31bac17eedec1fd5d3d922/2022-12/unknown_47585382_2378381535713075_6194992065767596893_n.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰近年的健康成為焦點。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9cea9368bedd5b7d934b283ec2340b07/2024-08/454003059_18351967606141665_563010136224334728_n.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰早前到台灣出席心靈講座，以幽默方式回應換心臟謠言。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/edc0d604f4d21127cdb33bed3371edf5/2026-03/604896368_18422163406141665_1590805320062590358_n.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"22歲的小女兒Jada也陪爸爸李連杰出席。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/28f7ea934e928530053c3eca27b1f3c7/2026-03/600216354_1406066240884879_3912793515260005644_n.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰昨日（26日）63歲生日。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a10936709a37b608b1fe619536398960/2026-04/Jet_1_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰獨自坐在餐枱前。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6f94a3dd18eee6ec0b949ef6d4a82f2b/2026-04/Jet_2_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰的細女準備驚喜。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f7983b1f3e271f3482733b68a53f2a80/2026-04/Jet_5_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"Jada將蠟燭插在父親李連杰的手指之間。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b4a92101257bed986dca1ea479fd63aa/2026-04/Jet_9_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"Jada點蠟燭。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e4800db5b9f5633a8e8dc89b0060b72b/2026-04/Jet_14_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"Jada將蠟燭抽出插到蛋糕上。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0b3eeb3c3de68e5fc1451c21e85b25c0/2026-04/Jet_24_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰睜開眼時嚇親。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ff1315cf8772e28e08d2b6350b245ff8/2026-04/Jet_29_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰金色彩紙從天而降，一臉驚喜。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/48c2c47a181f4b6b85b2b9bd058eb52d/2026-04/Jet_32_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰舉動好「少女味」濃。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ec7c27ae2deb31581e3c451a4250fbf9/2026-04/Jet_37_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰雙手合十許願。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b37d68f494a332192093d4d03fd19452/2026-04/Jet_40_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰吹蠟燭。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/220f60db0c89dc652ac62b6338644329/2026-04/Jet_49_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰全程心情大好，舉動活潑。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5237a291a7aff077bc1241c0b6239ef1/2026-04/Jet_56_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰對女兒安排表現讚揚。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cff8b0f7c8f66d3944d72865898f1309/2026-04/JET.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰2025年8月曾自爆入院：「最近又經歷了一次無常的試煉」。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/21eedeb7302a814d9b3a4cecd0d5e14f/2025-08/33_16.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰躺在病床雙眼緊閉，露出痛苦神情。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3abb14695d22d285617be40ef9f8ce33/2025-08/1106_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰在抖音報平安。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f070a8756dd59ab95037f8a78f6d8b53/2025-08/VS----0_00_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰早前坐輪椅。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/217f045d8b3ef48574faf88e619bb704/2025-08/VS----0_01__2.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰身處外國醫院。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8e3461601a8e8d2a3425ee042b89306d/2025-08/VS----0_05__1.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰要坐輪椅代步。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ee6d3ce645603b81e8987c3397cd05ed/2025-08/VS----0_14__0.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰氣色好轉。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/52dc3a168f63d137628049f775373931/2025-08/VS----0_18_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰頸部插喉管。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2b0e2fa83f216996154da2665438dad3/2025-08/VS----0_22_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"頸部喉管估計是用於輸鹽水或藥物。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/758c3c1521a63453947b9ece40bf216d/2025-08/VS----0_26__2.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰稱入院「修理」。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ee2cdeb659203aea088994ee0aa7c98f/2025-08/VS----0_28_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰已好返好多。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f17d146c9138249c90f1b0f653ce01e6/2025-08/VS----0_37_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰很快已經可以站起來。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6bbcf9b2c95ae9954be5f32677653012/2025-08/VS----0_50_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰3月時的狀態。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/753885dfdeec116b43b7e710ab452a41/2026-04/3_1_0_2.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰當時容光煥發。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/981bc7a5e4da45ca36da85a180228d81/2026-04/3_2_0_1.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰最近現身星洲法會。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4757ab07c52c84c21d1a1a8e67c9a8ed/2026-04/3_4_15.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰被見到臉色發黑。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/682b126bb297fe9eb97b8475818e6620/2026-04/1_0_12.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰面容憔悴。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e8f557c52e720ddb33f55a8f5bf687bd/2026-04/2_3_21.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰曾因傳出換心助回春傳聞，疑似用赤裸上身闢謠。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/30c2c3e8429cbe6498f93d901ce1118a/2025-11/a_1.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰上身不見有任何痕跡。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/af83a8fe931ccbd78ac37b866314a9b0/2025-11/c_0_0.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰畀埋背脊你睇。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d05793d3e211d2ce809a6920b8e2a804/2025-11/d_1.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰身材仍保持得不錯。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e56b59226695bd912fc9685ca3b9af14/2025-11/e.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰指做人應該有獨立思考。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/498163198a8788e3f046f8bdb7c4a89a/2025-11/f.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰再為換心換血一事澄清。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/66b26f0b6cefbb53c70a082cd2293ea6/2025-12/004_1.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰曾被拍得狀態麻麻。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/25605e5f36cfe2b6da5a30486f762f12/2025-11/g.jpg\"/>\n<h2>李連杰健康備受關注</h2>\n<p>李連杰近年的健康狀況，一直備受外界關注。李連杰在2013年因罹患甲狀腺功能亢進症（甲亢），需靠藥物控制病情，一度出現身形暴脹，外貌憔悴衰老。近年網上瘋傳李連杰「換心續命」、「飲童血回春」，要多度開腔闢謠。</p>\n<img alt=\"李連杰與利智育有兩女。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a9aa438b28f805ffe9ea3214ebf8f68a/2022-09/jetli_94835047_952675595149885_8575076924626305505_n.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"黃秋燕曾為李連杰誕下二女。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5b8a1d0ebe51ca1446d0aa2ccc38c6b3/2025-05/A20.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"有指李連杰將位於美國的住宅及財產給予黃秋燕。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/938bf9af2f4508a28b8c99294a301caf/2025-05/A1_13.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"黃秋燕曾為李連杰誕下二女。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/076c532f37ed152104ecafce8451118a/2025-05/A3_10.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"黃秋燕與李連杰結婚4年離婚。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0dedeeb409f75dfc42531f526599f0f1/2025-05/A4_7.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"黃秋燕昔日照片。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/db169086bf95e3e471279416169dd771/2025-05/A5_4.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"黃秋燕曾為李連杰誕下二女。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7968eee081e9ba88145b100060c3777c/2025-05/A22.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"網上曾流傳李連杰大女李思的照片。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/05d105bdd443117b8183fdd65af9ecb3/2025-08/imgi_91_i2172023.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰大女李思曾傳有意進軍娛樂圈。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4be119af17e26acbaed6d7012977c324/2025-08/imgi_6_i2172027.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰當年支持女兒入行。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/81b50bbad31169bfcc0108486cfa5836/2025-08/imgi_95_i2172028.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李苔蜜學有所成。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cb988cf70119ee61e05946b7df9268ef/2025-05/001nYKY0ly1i16plvdryzj62dc35sx6p02.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰二女李苔蜜是眼科醫生。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/afc82c87ef332ecef0850b9ef2e19aa6/2025-05/001nYKY0ly1i17w5xk9qzj62dc35s4qp02.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰曾為二女下廚。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9e09ac086dddaf3219ce042bffd0fbbf/2025-05/ec313fadgy1i18e30ko02j20k011ndje.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"今次李連杰為大女所選的車價值30萬人民幣。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d972acf613ade62254996b7343d38087/2025-08/002_3.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰與利智育有兩女。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a9aa438b28f805ffe9ea3214ebf8f68a/2022-09/jetli_94835047_952675595149885_8575076924626305505_n.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"利智的大女Jane畢業於美國哈佛大學，取得營養學士學位。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/35896c394c259d930ed526c96aca2258/2025-08/imgi.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰今年出席細女Jada大學畢業禮。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/97c872a5aba543d87c57a337fd14cdfa/2025-08/44_4.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"利智與李連杰於1988年因拍《龍在天涯》而結緣。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9ce82472cfb7b90f2941074a67d1ae76/2024-01/bKwh7stveMossD3HIf1y12OhIs5Frj0oNhx_3DYcf9w.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰與利智拍電影結緣後，秘密交往11年。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/06f9840549a7b98f6903b839774d06b2/2024-01/LEECHI_07.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰與利智結婚前，曾有過一段婚姻。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/affd6861133f443c5c82580d6233dc81/2022-12/lilianjie.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"有傳身家近20億港元的李連杰，早年曾公開稱現任妻子利智是其一生最愛。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/9d45e9ccd2c036642b7715823b5436e7/2024-01/LEECHI_08.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰與太太利智結婚多年，依然很恩愛。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/af40d04111eebedaf1ebc04cb4d4ee54/2022-12/unknown_94893589_123503659309970_1121304823310399006_n.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰晒出與兩個女兒的合照。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bb71edb272e88b33b942ad4cc5c4aa0b/2024-06/jetli_1_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰只上載利智的背面照。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aedfb9b038e5df1423076c9bbd33bf2a/2024-06/jetli_2_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰陪大女Jane及細女Jada去拉薩朝聖。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0b94f4c5a700d9b762f78e686cd0a6d6/2024-08/454011365_18351967594141665_6573758982830712043_n.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰與兩名女兒來到西藏。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7a8ff38be24f90bb2491f24413c91b98/2024-06/6abbdecd-b1ac-42bf-9371-b88dd5e9dac2.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李連杰一家四口曾到尼泊爾旅行，二女Jada當時晒出的利智（右）出鏡照，不是背影就是以黑超遮面。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1a696949f02ce252523b8a349968e5eb/2024-01/LEE_01.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"去年初網上流出一輯李連杰（右二）與妻女現身尼泊爾寺廟的照片。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ca4fb2cf20ff99bd7d97580951292c9f/2024-01/LEE_02.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"（左起）利智、女兒Jada和李連杰（右二）與住持一同合照。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cee0e719307490a6863f6c6e9499958c/2024-01/LEE_04.jpg\"/>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-27T05:25:52.266606+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":499,"images":72,"source":"星島頭條","fallback":"none"}}